&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Successful candidates will be invited to an Assessment Day on Friday 18th December 2020 . Please note this will be either a morning or afternoon session to be confirmed.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for motivated, enthusiastic and clinically capable registered nurses to join our team at Liskeard Community Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post is permanent and involves internal rotation, weekends and Bank Holidays. The successful applicant will be based on Willow ward at Liskeard Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Liskeard Community Hospital has an Outpatients Department, Operating Theatre and a Minor Injuries Unit. We provide step up and step down care and range from acute to rehabilitation. &lt;br /&gt;We require motivated, forward thinkers with a “can-do” attitude and a passion for nursing. In return we will support you in your career and involve you in the future development of services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ward Manager:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Willow: Karen Busher 01579 373531&lt;/p&gt;
